html(lang='en')
  head
    title PicoBudget - Expense tracking tool
    include includes/head.jade
  body
    include includes/nav.jade
    .container
      section#content
        .hero-unit
          h1 Easily manage your money
          p Ever wondered where your money goes? What do you spend the most money on? PicoBudget is a simple tool which features transactions, budgeting and reporting. Using Basic PicoBudget is absolutely free. If you enjoy it, though, you can get even more features with PicoBudget Premium!
          p Currently PicoBudget is under construction. Feel free to come back to check it out when it launched!

        .row
          .span4
            h2 Introduction
            p What is PicoBudget? Who is it for? Why should you use it?
            p
              a.btn.btn-info(href='http://localhost:1337/introduction') Read more &raquo;
